Package: MAGAR
Type: Package
Title: Package to compute methylation Quantitative Trait Loci (methQTL) from DNA methylation and genotyping data
Version: 0.3.6
Date: 2020-06-02
Authors@R: c(
	person("Scherer", "Michael", email="mscherer@mpi-inf.mpg.de", role=c("cre", "aut"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-7990-6179"))
	)
Maintainer: Michael Scherer <mscherer@mpi-inf.mpg.de>
Description: This package computes methQTL from DNA methylation and genotyping data from matched samples. It uses a
     linear modeling stragety to call CpGs/SNPs that form a methQTL that is aware of the local correlation structure
     of CpGs.
License: GPL-3
